{"type": "article", "id": 32192, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。PS：我们认为这个世界的重要性不应该有绝对的等级，重点是看得更多，探索更多。", "date": "2016-09-14T02:17:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160914101117i5FbD68wExRWU2AK.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><h3>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h3><p><b>1、金正恩在朝鲜核试验后首次亮相</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016091409375416abjElCYt4ksTAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666506\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Yonhap/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">据朝鲜《劳动新闻》报道，朝鲜最高领导人金正恩在朝鲜进行核试验后首次亮相，近日视察朝鲜人民军部队所属农场。<br></p><p><b>2、克什米尔地区冲突持续</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914093334VR5cpxCG0kql1PX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Danish Ismail/路透社/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">印控克什米尔斯利那加，当地民众在宰牲节期间与印度警察发生冲突，警察向示威者投放催泪弹。<br></p><p><b>3、聚焦美国总统大选</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914095130VBvPzuYcMb83hK6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Jessica Kourkounis/Getty Images/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">美国费城，美国总统奥巴马在当地发表演讲支持民主党总统候选人希拉里。9 月 11 日，希拉里在参加“9·11”纪念活动时因病退场，引发外界对她健康状况的再度关注。<br></p><p><b>4、关注寨卡病毒</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914093459hMcKiYm728Ot0Nw1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666571\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Athit Perawongmetha/路透社/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">泰国曼谷，卫生防疫人员在喷洒驱蚊烟雾。9 月 11 日在曼谷沙通地区又有 22 人确认感染寨卡病毒。<br></p><p><b>5、“海上联合-2016”联合军演</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914094250uV7NjYxEzhoOCtce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">李晋/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">广东省，参加“海上联合-2016”海上联合军演的中俄海军陆战队在某训练场联合演练了直升机滑降等训练科目。</p><h3>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h3><p class=\"\"><b>1、2017 纽约春夏时装周</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100957z1wMxcqoAkJ9smCD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Monica Schipper/Getty Images/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Zero + Maria Cornejo 后台，一名正在化妆的模特。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100719DX76Nznw2TvqRL98.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Astrid Stawiarz/Getty Images/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Thom Browne 后台。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914095418oDxH5zAq2K0pbVia.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666332\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Marie-Paola Bertrand-Hillion/Sipa USA/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914095620TqBJC6neuj7tl9Gk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Daniel Zuchnik/Getty Images/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">街头潮人云集。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2、军训</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914092730Ei8kTt0jfOxbqZCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">赵广亮/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">湖北省武汉市，中南财经政法大学首义校区大操场内，五千名新生身着迷彩服，高喊口号，在操场上进行夜晚队列训练。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>3、也门山村</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914092155lkbDNLSidyqzAmCs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Abduljabbar Zeyad/路透社/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">也门 Raymah 省 Jafariya，几名当地男孩在山上的池塘里游泳。Jafariya 是坐落在也门西部一座山上的村庄，居民们与席卷该国大部分地区的冲突保持着一个安全的距离，但是不得不以几个世纪前的生活方式度日。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>4、白化的珊瑚</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914091614uHyCPFq7N9iJTUtv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700965\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Kyodo News via Getty Images/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">日本冲绳县，航拍石垣岛和西表岛间的“石西礁湖”。因海水温度过高，这些珊瑚体内的彩色共生藻死亡或是离开珊瑚，导致这些珊瑚礁群出现大面积白化现象。若是水温持续升高，珊瑚将会永久死亡。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>5、由我掌镜</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914092524HynP21Irmdb7SUt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779724\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Giedrius Dalia Stakauskas/Solent News Agency/视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">英国伦敦，一只小狐狸闯入了摄影师的后院，并摆弄起了相机。<br></p>"}